params.name: input_ids
params.description: Indices of input sequence tokens in the vocabulary.Indices can be obtained using PreTrainedTokenizer. See PreTrainedTokenizer.encode() andPreTrainedTokenizer.call() for details.What are input IDs?

params.name: scores
params.description: Prediction scores of a language modeling head. These can be logits for each vocabulary when not using beamsearch or log softmax for each vocabulary token when using beam search
